00:39:15,319 --> 00:39:17,158
When Yi told me

567
00:39:17,719 --> 00:39:19,598
about Young Master Xiu's mole
at the mansion,

568
00:39:19,878 --> 00:39:20,719
I knew

569
00:39:21,479 --> 00:39:22,719
it would be Nan Ruzhen.

570
00:39:23,358 --> 00:39:24,559
However, I had no evidence.

571
00:39:25,519 --> 00:39:26,759
Any movement from Luo Qinglian?

572
00:39:26,918 --> 00:39:28,759
Xu Liangchuan has been keeping an eye.

573
00:39:29,118 --> 00:39:30,239
No movement at all.

574
00:39:30,999 --> 00:39:32,198
She is smart enough

575
00:39:33,559 --> 00:39:34,959
to have guessed something,

576
00:39:36,319 --> 00:39:37,799
but she doesn't tell Young Master anything.

577
00:39:40,279 --> 00:39:41,838
What is she up to?

578
00:39:43,198 --> 00:39:43,959
Could she have

579
00:39:44,319 --> 00:39:46,198
something on us

580
00:39:46,438 --> 00:39:47,438
and she wants to threaten us?

581
00:39:52,398 --> 00:39:53,519
We can never control

582
00:39:54,838 --> 00:39:56,319
what others want to do.

583
00:39:58,438 --> 00:39:59,759
The most brilliant way

584
00:40:00,959 --> 00:40:02,039
is to invalidate

585
00:40:03,319 --> 00:40:04,598
what she has on us.

586
00:40:08,239 --> 00:40:09,398
Poor living condition

587
00:40:09,999 --> 00:40:10,918
and others' taunting

588
00:40:10,918 --> 00:40:11,999
don't matter.

589
00:40:12,678 --> 00:40:14,079
Young Master matters the most.

590
00:40:17,079 --> 00:40:18,799
I need this if I can't win

591
00:40:22,358 --> 00:40:23,279
Young Master's heart.

592
00:40:23,678 --> 00:40:25,079
As long as I conceive a child,

593
00:40:30,039 --> 00:40:31,358
I would like to see

594
00:40:33,598 --> 00:40:35,559
who can stop me.

595
00:40:37,719 --> 00:40:38,398
Lian'er.

596
00:40:39,118 --> 00:40:41,079
Why you don't tell Young Master everything?

597
00:40:54,878 --> 00:40:56,759
I haven't told Young Master about this.

598
00:40:57,479 --> 00:40:59,398
I didn't even mention

599
00:40:59,438 --> 00:41:00,759
Nan Ruzhen's act

600
00:41:01,810 --> 00:41:03,239
of causing my miscarriage
and stopping him.

601
00:41:04,118 --> 00:41:05,559
Do you know why?

602
00:41:08,959 --> 00:41:10,118
Neither the miscarriage

603
00:41:10,118 --> 00:41:11,039
nor her identity as a mole

604
00:41:11,479 --> 00:41:13,759
can be proven with solid evidence.

605
00:41:14,559 --> 00:41:15,398
Since Young Master

606
00:41:15,559 --> 00:41:17,118
takes Nan Ruzhen as a bosom friend,

607
00:41:17,918 --> 00:41:19,438
he would forgive her

608
00:41:19,438 --> 00:41:20,519
a few more times

609
00:41:20,519 --> 00:41:21,519
after once or twice.

610
00:41:22,198 --> 00:41:24,398
I have not much of a chance to try.

611
00:41:26,158 --> 00:41:28,118
The evidence must be enough conclusive
to defeat her.

612
00:41:29,279 --> 00:41:31,638
However, if I say nothing,

613
00:41:33,279 --> 00:41:35,878
Nan Ruzhen will be uneasy, as if having

614
00:41:35,878 --> 00:41:36,959
a fish bone stuck in her throat.

615
00:41:39,279 --> 00:41:40,799
Even a worm will turn.

616
00:41:43,598 --> 00:41:44,519
I'm sure

617
00:41:45,050 --> 00:41:46,470
she'll end up providing
me with a chance.

618
00:42:00,060 --> 00:42:03,700
♪From the chaotic dust♪

619
00:42:03,700 --> 00:42:05,920
♪Gracefully stepping out♪

620
00:42:07,080 --> 00:42:10,150
♪Only then did I understand
the beauty of the world♪

621
00:42:10,790 --> 00:42:13,180
♪Why, and for what♪

622
00:42:14,130 --> 00:42:17,380
♪Holding pure intentions
in my heart♪

623
00:42:17,750 --> 00:42:20,560
♪Clinging to black and white♪

624
00:42:21,210 --> 00:42:24,040
♪Only then did I realize
that the path is simple♪

625
00:42:24,600 --> 00:42:27,120
♪It is love♪

626
00:42:27,990 --> 00:42:29,590
♪When fate♪

627
00:42:30,000 --> 00:42:32,830
♪Surges like deep clouds♪

628
00:42:35,070 --> 00:42:36,840
♪Regardless of♪

629
00:42:37,280 --> 00:42:38,760
♪What experiences may come♪

630
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:43,680
♪Unable to linger♪

631
00:42:44,190 --> 00:42:46,160
♪Mountains and waves
are insignificant♪

632
00:42:46,160 --> 00:42:48,750
♪My promises to you remain♪

633
00:42:50,920 --> 00:42:54,600
♪Unafraid of obstacles
along this worldly path♪

634
00:42:54,900 --> 00:42:57,150
♪Worries are few♪

635
00:42:58,440 --> 00:43:00,270
♪The moon sets, stars scatter,
and mournful sounds ring♪

636
00:43:00,270 --> 00:43:04,010
♪My promises to you remain♪

637
00:43:04,900 --> 00:43:07,940
♪Life after life♪

638
00:43:09,040 --> 00:43:11,640
♪Will follow my heart's desires♪

639
00:43:13,440 --> 00:43:15,250
♪Forever unchanged♪
